Module org.phenopackets.phenopackettools.core

Package org.phenopackets.phenopackettools.core

package org.phenopackets.phenopackettools.core
A package with constants and types used across the entire application, including the base exception classes.

The package contains the base checked exception PhenopacketToolsException and unchecked exception PhenopacketToolsRuntimeException.

Several useful enumerations complete the circle:

  • PhenopacketElement
  • PhenopacketFormat
  • PhenopacketSchemaVersion
  • Class
    Description
    PhenopacketElement
    The enum members represent the top-level elements of the Phenopacket schema.
    PhenopacketFormat
    The enum members represent the supported representations of the top-level elements of the Phenopacket schema.
    PhenopacketSchemaVersion
    An enum with currently supported Phenopacket schema versions.
    PhenopacketToolsException
    Base checked exception thrown by phenopacket-tools.
    PhenopacketToolsRuntimeException
    Base unchecked exception thrown by phenopacket-tools.
